name: Exsoular
description:
I AM NOT THE ORIGINAL CREATOR OF THIS MODEL

This model is originally from HuggingFace but appears to no longer be there. It's a great model, so it's a shame to have it lost to the void so I've reuploaded it here. What sets it apart from some of the other models is it has a nice distinctive outline and softer colors that work well depending on the goals you have for your image

If the original creator or Civit mods etc want it removed let me know and I'll take it down
